FT  27 MAR 92 / Election 1992: No picture - Ballot Box
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
William Waldegrave, health secretary, was poised for a photo opportunity at
Central Office yesterday, along with a group of about 30 doctors who support
the National Health Service reforms.
Photographers downed cameras, however, when the doctors turned out in suits,
not white coats. 'They could have been anyone,' said one.
