<HEADLINE>
FT  27 MAR 92 / World News in Brief: Cricket deaths
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
At least five people were killed by stray bullets when cricket fans in
Pakistan celebrated their country's World Cup victory over England by firing
weapons in the air.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
International Page 1
</PAGE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>FT921-876</DOCNO>
<PROFILE>_AN-CC3BAAAAFT</PROFILE>
<DATE>920327
